episodes.title: Excellent Clearwater Scientology Testimony -  Janie Peterson
episodes.description: Janie Peterson worked in the Guardians Office and offers some great insight into much of Scientology's covert workings. This is from the Clearwater Hearings of 1982. It appears that not much has changed.

episodes.title: Affidavit of Carol Garrity read into Clearwater record
episodes.description: This is an affidavit from Carol Garrity being read into the record. She worked in the Guardians Office

episodes.title: Casey Kelly - 1982 Scientology Hearings in Clearwater
episodes.description: Casey Kelly handled Recruitment and Finances for Scientology. For three years. It seems that not much  has changed in the cult over the years.
